icarbonate有啲分別，唔知bicarbonate效果係點）<br />\n<br />\n2.消毒火酒（酒精）/含消毒火酒成份濕紙巾<br />\n<br />\n3.化妝水/卸妝水/洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n可以洗到有acrylics/PMMA嘅顏料<br />\n<br />\n紅字係考慮完availability, effectiveness, usefulness, side-effects嘅建議<br />\n<br />\n另外衫褲鞋襪可以先噴防水噴霧<br />\n中招就唔好留直接dum咗佢<br />\n<br />\n消毒火酒：<br />\n易買 平 可用作消毒 但係多用傷皮膚<br />\n化/卸妝水：<br />\n女仔會有 比較唔傷皮膚 但貴 同埋唔同牌子效果可能會有差異<br />\n<br />\n其他建議：<br />\n#67 威猛先生玻璃劑<br />\n#91 含酒精成分濕紙巾<br />\n#117 大塊顏料可以待乾再成塊搣<br />\n<br />\n#127<br />\n可以搽定凡士林/hand cream<br />\n保持皮膚濕潤方便移除顏料<br />\n<br />\n#145<br />\n唔敢去五金可以去模型舖買Mr Color paint remover/Mr Color tool cleaner，冇就買住水性油天拿水頂住先<br />\n<br />\n#148<br />\n補充使用順序：<br />\n先用水性油天拿水或者75%酒精捽<br />\n好頑固捽唔到嗰啲先用paint remover/tool cleaner<br />\n因為用完呢兩隻，啲顏料會變硝基，用唔返酒精<br />\n最後都唔得先好用洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n#164<br />\n凡士林coating，logon $50 gel removal<br />\n<br />\n#216<br />\n應該冇加料 UV燈照過安全，番簡水、梳打水可行"},{"pid":"8c9e0718398e662db4162d00c1e7fdd550136180","tid":1522063,"uid":312228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:13:58.000Z","msg":"仍在埸的手足要小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efae5caec9e1318ceaf169a656689eea112628c2","tid":1522063,"uid":74935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:14:18.000Z","msg":"又被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bd24fdbc06081a5416add1ef7a8e972334b2fce","tid":1522063,"uid":28771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:15:36.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"3c28e38b8c42976a4354383a0906a4a8ece88d34","tid":1522063,"uid":70313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:17:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e90df7dba220f3e5bab0a4ebb04aafc7edf6d6f","tid":1522063,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:17:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"914f27812f34908671dfb6ea9e0417a0d43c7019","tid":1522063,"uid":240522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0